"version": "1.0.4",
"title": "4464: harvest",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4464",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The gathering of mature crops from the land. The successful culmination of the agricultural year was evidence of God's goodness and consequently marked with festivity. Harvest is also used widely in a metaphorical sense.</p>\n<h2>The harvest is evidence of God's goodness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:22\">GEN 8:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:10\">2CO 9:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:5\">LEV 26:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:9-Lev26:10\">LEV 26:9–26:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps67:6\">PSA 67:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps85:12\">PSA 85:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:37\">PSA 107:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:8-Isa62:9\">ISA 62:8–62:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:24\">JER 5:24</a></p>\n<h2>Laws relating to the harvest</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:10-Exod23:11\">EXO 23:10–23:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:21\">EXO 34:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:9\">LEV 19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:23-Lev19:25\">LEV 19:23–19:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:22\">LEV 23:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:4-Lev25:5\">LEV 25:4–25:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:11-Lev25:12\">LEV 25:11–25:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:18-Lev25:27\">LEV 25:18–25:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:12-Num18:13\">NUM 18:12–18:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:19-Deut24:21\">DEU 24:19–24:21</a></p>\n<h2>Harvest festivals</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:16\">EXO 23:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:22\">EXO 34:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:10-Lev23:16\">LEV 23:10–23:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:33-Lev23:43\">LEV 23:33–23:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:13-Deut16:15\">DEU 16:13–16:15</a></p>\n<h2>Harvest marked times of the year</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:22\">RUT 1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh3:15\">JOS 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:1\">JDG 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:13\">1SA 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:17\">1SA 12:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:9-2Sam21:10\">2SA 21:9–21:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:13\">2SA 23:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:20\">JER 8:20</a></p>\n<h2>Characteristics of harvest</h2>\n<h3>Rejoicing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:3\">ISA 9:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:5-Ps126:6\">PSA 126:5–126:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:9\">ISA 16:9</a></p>\n<h3>Hard work</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:5\">PRO 10:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:4\">PRO 14:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:4\">PRO 20:4</a></p>\n<h2>Failed harvests are a sign of God's judgment</h2>\n<h3>Poor harvests</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:13\">JER 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:10-Isa17:11\">ISA 17:10–17:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:10\">ISA 32:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:13\">JER 8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:11\">JOL 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:7\">AMO 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:15\">MIC 6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:6\">HAG 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>Others eating the harvest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:17\">JER 5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:37\">NEH 9:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:5\">JOB 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:12\">JOB 31:12</a></p>\n<h2>The metaphorical use of harvest</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:13\">JOL 3:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:37-Matt9:38\">MAT 9:37–9:38</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:9\">GAL 6:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:15-Rev14:16\">REV 14:15–14:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:20\">PRO 18:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:13\">PRO 25:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:1\">PRO 26:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:5\">ISA 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa18:4-Isa18:5\">ISA 18:4–18:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:13\">ISA 24:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:4\">ISA 28:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:4\">ISA 33:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:3\">JER 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:33\">JER 51:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:11\">HOS 6:11</a>MAT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:30\">13:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:39\">MAT 13:39</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:24\">MAT 25:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:29\">MRK 4:29</a> <em>the parable of the growing seed</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:1-Mark12:9\">MRK 12:1–12:9</a> <em>the parable of the tenants</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:2\">LUK 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:35-John4:36\">JHN 4:35–4:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:13\">ROM 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:10-1Cor9:11\">1CO 9:10–9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:11\">HEB 12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:18\">JAS 3:18</a></p>",
